(1112, 2430, 'mfn-page-items-seo', '<img src="http://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/famservice-headlrg.jpg" alt="famservice-headlrg"/>\n\ncenter\n\n<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />\r\nFREE Cargo Van Wash EVERY Saturday! Get a free wash for your cargo van, no purchase necessary! Just bring your cargo van down any Saturday and we''ll get it cleaned up for you. **First come first serve, only during business hours, subject to availability of staff, cargo vans only**\n\nleft\n\nhttp://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/famservice-freewash.jpg\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\ncontain\n\nfont-size:16px;\n\n<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />\r\nFREE Oil Change for your cargo van only at FAM Vans! Print out a copy of this page and bring it down with your cargo van to receive a free oil change! Limit one free oil change on gasoline engines per customer. First come first serve, only during business hours, subject to availability of staff, cargo vans only, Call in advance to book an appointment**\n\nleft\n\nhttp://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/freeoilchangelrg.jpg\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\ncontain\n\nfont-size:16px;\n\n<img class="scale-with-grid" src="#" alt="" />FAM Vans service department is a fully licensed repair facility that specializes in cargo vans, box trucks, and all other commercial vehicles. We will assist your business with all of its fleet servicing needs. Our ASE certified technicians are known as "The Cargo Van Experts." \r\n\r\nWith more than ten years experience, our team of trained and fully qualified technicians will repair your fleet of cargo vans, box trucks, or other commercial vehicle at the lowest prices in town. Be assured FAM Vans will exceed the standard when it comes down to mechanical repairs. Our fleet maintenance program goes beyond good prices and satisfactory service, we strive to make the experience the best you''ve ever had, and return your commercial vehicle with the best in performance and safety.\r\n<center><img class="scale-with-grid" src="http://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/ASE_logo2.jpg" alt="famvans" /></center>\r\nFAM Vans truly does have the best prices in town, but if you do happen to find a lower price, WE''LL BEAT IT! Any service work at any advertised price you find, we''re ready to get the job done. Not only does FAM Vans have the best service department around, able to take care of just about any service need you request, but we also back up all our work with a 100% satisfaction guarantee! Contact a service rep today for more information: 877.932.6826	\r\n<center><img class="scale-with-grid" src="http://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/famservice-beatprice.jpg" alt="" /></center>\r\n<center><img class="scale-with-grid" src="http://famvans.autocomp.biz/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/famservice-100gurantee.jpg" alt="" /></center>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 20%\n\nNEW SERVICE BUILDING NOW OPEN!\n\nMonday - Friday 8:00am to 6:00pm,  Saturday 8:00am to 1:00pm,  Closed on Sunday\n\nline\n\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3318.918009155069!2d-117.93459354847081!3d33.711070442982944!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x80dd275db5d31701%3A0xb8b72f1d272d862d!2s17370+Mt+Herrmann+St%2C+Fountain+Valley%2C+CA+92708!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1506125901179" width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),
